#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an4.67"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.67:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.67:0.2"
msgid "7. Pattakammavagga "
msgstr "7. Deeds of Substance "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: ahi (metta) suttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.67:0.3"
msgid "67. Ahirājasutta "
msgstr "67. The Snake King "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an4.67:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.67:1.2"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena sāvatthiyaṃ aññataro bhikkhu ahinā daṭṭho kālaṅkato hoti. "
msgstr "Now, at that time a monk in Sāvatthī passed away due to a snake bite. "

msgctxt "an4.67:1.3"
msgid "Atha kho sambahulā bhikkhū yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu. Ekamantaṃ nisinnā kho te bhikkhū bhagavantaṃ etadavocuṃ: "
msgstr "Then several mendicants went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, and said to him, "

msgctxt "an4.67:1.4"
msgid "“idha, bhante, sāvatthiyaṃ aññataro bhikkhu ahinā daṭṭho kālaṅkato”ti. "
msgstr "“Sir, a monk in Sāvatthī has passed away due to a snake bite.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
#. VAR: Na hi nūna → nahanūna (bj, s1, s2, km, pts1) | naha nūna (s3)
msgctxt "an4.67:2.1"
msgid "“Na hi nūna so, bhikkhave, bhikkhu cattāri ahirājakulāni mettena cittena phari. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, that monk mustn’t have spread a mind of love to the four royal snake families. "

msgctxt "an4.67:2.2"
msgid "Sace hi so, bhikkhave, bhikkhu cattāri ahirājakulāni mettena cittena phareyya, na hi so, bhikkhave, bhikkhu ahinā daṭṭho kālaṃ kareyya. "
msgstr "If he had, he wouldn’t have died due to a snake bite. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an4.67:3.1"
msgid "Katamāni cattāri? "
msgstr "What four? "

msgctxt "an4.67:3.2"
msgid "Virūpakkhaṃ ahirājakulaṃ, erāpathaṃ ahirājakulaṃ, chabyāputtaṃ ahirājakulaṃ, kaṇhāgotamakaṃ ahirājakulaṃ. "
msgstr "The royal snake families of Virūpakkha, Erāpatha, Chabyāputta, and Kaṇhāgotamaka. … "

msgctxt "an4.67:3.3"
msgid "Na hi nūna so, bhikkhave, bhikkhu imāni cattāri ahirājakulāni mettena cittena phari. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.67:3.4"
msgid "Sace hi so, bhikkhave, bhikkhu imāni cattāri ahirājakulāni mettena cittena phareyya, na hi so, bhikkhave, bhikkhu ahinā daṭṭho kālaṃ kareyya. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an4.67:4.1"
msgid "Anujānāmi, bhikkhave, imāni cattāri ahirājakulāni mettena cittena pharituṃ attaguttiyā attarakkhāya attaparittāyāti. "
msgstr "Mendicants, I urge you to spread a mind of love to the four royal snake families, for your own safety, security, and protection. "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "an4.67:5.1"
msgid "Virūpakkhehi me mettaṃ, "
msgstr "I love the Virūpakkhas, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.67:5.2"
msgid "Mettaṃ erāpathehi me; "
msgstr "the Erāpathas I love, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.67:5.3"
msgid "Chabyāputtehi me mettaṃ, "
msgstr "I love the Chabyāputtas, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.67:5.4"
msgid "Mettaṃ kaṇhāgotamakehi ca. "
msgstr "the Kaṇhāgotamakas I love. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.73, sc6
msgctxt "an4.67:6.1"
msgid "Apādakehi me mettaṃ, "
msgstr "I love the footless creatures, "

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: dvipādakehi → dipādakehi (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "an4.67:6.2"
msgid "mettaṃ dvipādakehi me; "
msgstr "the two-footed I love, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.67:6.3"
msgid "Catuppadehi me mettaṃ, "
msgstr "I love the four-footed, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.67:6.4"
msgid "mettaṃ bahuppadehi me. "
msgstr "the many-footed I love. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc7
msgctxt "an4.67:7.1"
msgid "Mā maṃ apādako hiṃsi, "
msgstr "May the footless not harm me! "

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: dvipādako → dipādako (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "an4.67:7.2"
msgid "mā maṃ hiṃsi dvipādako; "
msgstr "May I not be harmed by the two-footed! "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.67:7.3"
msgid "Mā maṃ catuppado hiṃsi, "
msgstr "May the four-footed not harm me! "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.67:7.4"
msgid "mā maṃ hiṃsi bahuppado. "
msgstr "May I not be harmed by the many-footed! "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc8
msgctxt "an4.67:8.1"
msgid "Sabbe sattā sabbe pāṇā, "
msgstr "All sentient beings, all living things, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.67:8.2"
msgid "sabbe bhūtā ca kevalā; "
msgstr "all creatures, every one: "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.67:8.3"
msgid "Sabbe bhadrāni passantu, "
msgstr "may they see only nice things, "

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: kañci → kiñci (s1-3, km, mr)
msgctxt "an4.67:8.4"
msgid "mā kañci pāpamāgamā. "
msgstr "may bad not come to anyone. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc9
msgctxt "an4.67:9.1"
msgid "Appamāṇo buddho, "
msgstr "The Buddha is immeasurable, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.67:9.2"
msgid "Appamāṇo dhammo; "
msgstr "the teaching is immeasurable, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.67:9.3"
msgid "Appamāṇo saṃgho, "
msgstr "the Saṅgha is immeasurable. "

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: sarīsapāni → siriṃsapāni (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "an4.67:9.4"
msgid "Pamāṇavantāni sarīsapāni. "
msgstr "But limited are crawling things, "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc10
msgctxt "an4.67:10.1"
msgid "Ahivicchikā satapadī, "
msgstr "snakes and scorpions, centipedes, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.67:10.2"
msgid "Uṇṇanābhī sarabū mūsikā; "
msgstr "spiders and lizards and mice. "

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: rakkhā katā me parittā → kataṃ me parittaṃ (?)
msgctxt "an4.67:10.3"
msgid "Katā me rakkhā katā me parittā, "
msgstr "I’ve made this safeguard, I’ve made this protection: "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.67:10.4"
msgid "Paṭikkamantu bhūtāni; "
msgstr "go away, creatures! "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.67:10.5"
msgid "Sohaṃ namo bhagavato, "
msgstr "And so I revere the Blessed One, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.67:10.6"
msgid "Namo sattannaṃ sammāsambuddhānan”ti. "
msgstr "I revere the seven perfectly awakened Buddhas.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.67:10.7"
msgid "Sattamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
